suggestions.original: To improve the color contrast in the artwork, consider intensifying the colors of the kennel and pillow. For example, using a deeper orange or a more vibrant yellow can make these elements stand out more. Additionally, enhancing the blue of the collar to a brighter or more saturated shade can further draw attention to it. Adding some darker shades or outlines around the dog and other elements can also help to create a more striking visual impact.
